title: Bug 109350: Output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog
description: The output parameter is not being displayed in the edit data set dialog when in the query result page.
OB: While on the query result page, there is no data returned. The actual result is that the output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
1. Navigate to the query result page.
2. Execute a query that has an output parameter.
3. Open the edit data set dialog and verify that the output parameter is displayed.
